FT  11 NOV 92 / UK Company News: Hartlepools Water falls to Pounds 670,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pre-tax profits of Hartlepools Water Company slipped by 3 per cent, from
Pounds 690,000 to Pounds 670,000, in the six months to end-September.
The company said the recession continued to depress metered demand by
industrial customers.
Turnover rose slightly, from Pounds 2.59m to Pounds 2.61m, and earnings per
stock unit increased to 67p (66p). The interim dividend is raised to 22p
(21p).
