cashflow problems - In a Nutshell
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Poor cashflow management has been one of the main factors behind business
failures in the present recession.
Financing the Credit Gap*, a new guide produced by Griffin Factors and the
CBI, contains advice, examples, checklists and charts to help ease and
predict cashflow and profits.
